f=Engineering/dev/custom/code-review-standards/assets/stack-notes-typescript-node-2026-07.md · h1:Stack Notes TypeScript/JavaScript Conventions (dated 2026-07)=**Applies business's stack-profile names TypeScript/JavaScript (Node, React, Next.js).** Method authority: `code-review-standards` (this note feeds style correctness steps). Source: affaan-m/everything-claude-code `coding-standards`, adopted 2026-07-10, condensed. Re-verify against ecosystem norms months old. · h2:Universal floor (stack-agnostic already enforced code-review-standards)=Readability first KISS DRY YAGNI early returns over deep nesting (≤3 levels) magic numbers (named constants) functions ≤~50 lines comments explain WHAT. · h2:TypeScript/JavaScript specifics=**Naming:** descriptive (`marketSearchQuery` `q`); functions verb-noun (`fetchMarketData`, `isValidEmail`); booleans `is/has/can` prefixed., **Immutability (critical):** spread over mutation `{...user, name}` `[...items, newItem]`; never `obj.x `arr.push()` shared state. Deliberate mutation performance gets comment., **No `any`:** proper interfaces; closed sets union literals (`'active' 'resolved'`)., **Error handling:** `fetch`/IO wrapped check `response.ok`, throw status context; never bare `response.json()`., **Async:** `Promise.all` independent awaits sequential awaits dependent., **Files:** components PascalCase (`Button.tsx`) hooks `useX.ts` utils camelCase types `*.types.ts`., **JSDoc public APIs:** params, returns, throws, example. · h2:React specifics (review checklist)=Typed props interfaces defaults functional state updates (`setCount(prev prev 1)`, never stale `count 1`) custom hooks reused logic (e.g. `useDebounce`) `&&`-chains over nested ternaries conditional rendering. · te:ing style=AAA structure (Arrange-Act-Assert) descriptive names ("returns empty array match", never "works") quinn's test-strategy owns gate; per-review style check. · h2:API-route style (raj's api-standards contract authority)=Consistent `{success, data?, error?, meta?}` envelope schema validation (e.g. Zod) handler edge, 400 details failure.